OL,3,CPublic must 'see the evidence' in
OL,4,CNottingham attack inquiry, families say
OL,6,FFamilies of the Nottingham attack
OL,7,Fvictims have said the public deserves
OL,8,Fto see the evidence for themselves
OL,9,Fwhen a major inquiry begins next year,
OL,10,Fcalling for hearings to be broadcast
OL,11,Flive to ensure transparency.
OL,13,FValdo Calocane killed University of
OL,14,FNottingham students Barnaby Webber and
OL,15,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,16,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, before
OL,17,Fattempting to kill three other people
OL,18,Fin the city in June 2023.
