OL,3,CPublic must 'see the evidence' in
OL,4,CNottingham attack inquiry, families say
OL,6,FThe public inquiry, chaired by senior
OL,7,Fretired judge Deborah Taylor, is
OL,8,Fexpected to begin substantive hearings
OL,9,Finto the attacks on February 23 2026
OL,10,Fand aims to report back within two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FAt the first preliminary hearing on
OL,14,FFriday, Ms Taylor received submissions
OL,15,Fon behalf of survivors, people
OL,16,Fbereaved by the attacks, as well as
OL,17,Fmultiple public bodies and the media
OL,18,Fover whether there should be
OL,19,Flivestream access to the proceedings
OL,20,Fand whether they should be broadcast.
