OL,3,CPublic must 'see the evidence' in
OL,4,CNottingham attack inquiry, families say
OL,6,FTim Moloney KC, on behalf of the
OL,7,Fbereaved families, said there could be
OL,8,F"public surprise and disappointment"
OL,9,Fif there was no remote way to observe
OL,10,Fthe hearing ` which will take place in
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,FHe said: "There is a great public
OL,14,Finterest in these proceedings which
OL,15,Fcould be satisfied by a live stream
OL,16,Fbut there is also a public interest in
OL,17,Fensuring that material that should not
OL,18,Fbe live streamed is not live streamed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
