OL,3,CPublic must 'see the evidence' in
OL,4,CNottingham attack inquiry, families say
OL,6,F"Where it is possible to broadcast
OL,7,Fevidence and have the public make
OL,8,Ftheir own mind up, we say the public
OL,9,Fshould be able to see that evidence,"
OL,10,Fhe added.
OL,12,FMr Moloney continued: "For those who
OL,13,Fwere bereaved on June 13 2023, the
OL,14,Fwork of this inquiry is critical."
OL,16,FMs Taylor is expected to give her
OL,17,Fdecision on whether the proceedings
OL,18,Fcan be live streamed or broadcast on
OL,19,FNovember 10.
