OL,3,CPublic must 'see the evidence' in
OL,4,CNottingham attack inquiry, families say
OL,6,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,8,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,10,Fattempted murder.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Justice previously
OL,13,Fsaid the management of Calocane's risk
OL,14,Fto others in the lead-up to the
OL,15,Fattacks and public servants accessing
OL,16,Finformation without authorisation will
OL,17,Fform part of the inquiry.
